      "id": "PopularPost290295",
      "post_content": "I'd prefer this to playing two [Stone Rain](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Stone Rain)s. With this alone, you get the chance to 2-for-1 an opponent. So this comes with card advantage. The same can't be said for two Stone Rains.  \n  \nOf course, in the kind of deck that runs this, you're probably running both, along with [Wake of Destruction](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Wake of Destruction).",
